Teaching and Research in [[Germany |German]] [[American studies]] is mostly done on the level of [[University |universities]]. Many [[English Studies]] departments have one or more [[professor | professorships]] designated as "Amerikanistik" or "Amerikastudien." Some universities offer full American studies programs or even have individual American studies [[Academic department |departments]] consisting of several, specialized professorships and an individual [[budget]].
==Information== On a national level, the German Association for American Studies (Deutsche Gesellschaft für Amerikastudien, DGfA<ref>Homepage of the [http://www.dgfa.de Deutsche Gesellschaft für Amerikastudien]</ref>) organizes annual conventions and smaller local congresses.
The most important periodical publishing venue is the quarterly "Amerikastudien American Studies,"<ref>[http://amerikastudien.de/quarterly/index.html Homepage of the journal]</ref> the official publication organ of the German Association for American Studies.
